Generic single-database configuration for NatalNanny.

Run from `backend/` with the virtualenv active:

  pip install -r requirements.txt
  python -m alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe change"
  python -m alembic upgrade head
  python -m alembic downgrade -1

Use `python -m alembic` (not bare `alembic`) so the project venv is used,
not a globally installed Alembic on another Python.

`DATABASE_URL` is read from app settings (`.env` or env vars).
